---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Social Network | The Agora App" description="The last social app you'll ever need. Built for real-world coordination.">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 bg-olive-50 text-olive-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-700 font-bold">
        Project: The Agora App
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-olive-950">
        The last social app <br/> <span class="text-amber-600">you’ll ever need.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-olive-800 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-serif italic">
        No algorithm. No infinite scroll. No data mining. Just a digital bridge to your local physical community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      
      <div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-olive-50 border border-olive-100 space-y-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-900">For Members</h2>
        <p class="text-olive-700 leading-relaxed">
          The app functions as a <strong>Local Bulletin Board</strong>. Find where your chapter is meeting, RSVP for events, and see announcements from your Sponsor. It opens, gives you what you need, and encourages you to close it.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium text-olive-800">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Neighborhood Event Map
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Secure RSVP & Check-in
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Peer-to-Peer “Analog Exchanges”
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-olive-900 border border-olive-800 space-y-6 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 bg-amber-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">For Chapter Leaders</h2>
        <p class="text-olive-200 leading-relaxed">
          A powerful <strong>Coordination Hub</strong>. Manage your local cell, track attendance, and sync with Quorum. It’s the logistics layer that keeps the movement moving forward without the noise.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium text-olive-100">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-olive-800 border border-olive-700 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Member Lifecycle Management
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-olive-800 border border-olive-700 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Direct Sync with Regional Nodes
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-olive-800 border border-olive-700 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 text-[10px]">✔</span>
            Leader-to-Leader Strategy Channels
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 text-center bg-olive-50">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-olive-950 tracking-tight">Join the Beta</h2>
      <p class="text-olive-700 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We are rolling out the Agora App chapter by chapter to prioritize high-trust coordination over mass-market scale.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-4">
        <a href="/#cta" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-amber-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-amber-600/20 active:scale-95 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
          Apply for Member Access
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>